The <a href="Mushroom_cloud" title="Mushroom cloud">mushroom cloud</a> of the <a href="Atomic_bombings_of_Hiroshima_and_Nagasaki" title="Atomic bombings of Hiroshima and Nagasaki">atomic bombing of Nagasaki, Japan</a> on August 9, 1945 rose some 18 kilometers (11&#160;mi) above the bomb's <a href="Hypocenter" title="Hypocenter">hypocenter</a>.</div>
